    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《维京——北欧之地传奇</strong>》是一款<strong>等角2D城市建造</strong>游戏，根植于维京时代，基于老派网格系统，允许你建造和管理你的北方城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在北欧风光中，<strong>重温维京273年的历史</strong>，从793年首次袭击林迪斯法恩大修道院到1066年斯坦福桥战役。 管理<strong>北欧文化</strong>的各个方面<strong>，带领你的人民走向伟大</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/c4663710db1fed69e9e77fc2639bb3bd.avif?t=1771452519\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/d762adbad5cd9d5bc276b65ae97bb537.poster.avif?t=1771452519\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/d762adbad5cd9d5bc276b65ae97bb537.webm?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/d762adbad5cd9d5bc276b65ae97bb537.mp4?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>建造最伟大的维京城市</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《维京传奇——北欧传奇》延续<strong>了2000年代首批城市建设游戏</strong>的基本玩法。在近三百年的历史中设计并建造属于自己的城市。一条路，一条房子，一口水井......冒险可以开始了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/87721463895d48644cefe552fb93ffd5.avif?t=1771452519\" width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5b6e6ca29ae2f8153b1e5ae38f82145b.poster.avif?t=1771452519\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5b6e6ca29ae2f8153b1e5ae38f82145b.webm?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5b6e6ca29ae2f8153b1e5ae38f82145b.mp4?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>收割、转化和管理你的资源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立多条生产线</strong> ，为你的市民提供所需的一切。在农场种植小麦，在磨坊中将其加工成面粉，烤面包养活你的人民。 <strong>用资源</strong> 满足需求或 <strong>与其他城市贸易</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/87721463895d48644cefe552fb93ffd5.avif?t=1771452519\" width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5245b07d0a5c815428d27b3909219c2e.poster.avif?t=1771452519\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5245b07d0a5c815428d27b3909219c2e.webm?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/5245b07d0a5c815428d27b3909219c2e.mp4?t=1771452519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>直观且易于访问的界面</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《维京人》——《北欧传奇》的界面设计旨在即时理解。侧面板汇集了所有必要信息，并让你快速访问<strong>与每个类别相关的</strong>建筑和管理数据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/c4663710db1fed69e9e77fc2639bb3bd.avif?t=1771452519\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《维京人——北欧传奇》包含许多特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个老派的等角网格 </strong>建设系统，会带你回到最初的城市建设者时代</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理 </strong>你所在人口的需求（食物、文化、健康、安全等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集</strong>资源，转化它们，用于需求或贸易。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>许多建筑已开放 </strong>（抢先体验期间将有更多内容）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大地图可以 </strong>让你建造令人印象深刻的城市</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立一个政府</strong>，管理公民工资并征税</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>像素艺术图形</strong>，配合大量动画，制作得非常用心！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>得益于其在环境中的位置</strong>，营造出沉浸式的声音景观！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原创中世纪/北欧音乐原声带</strong>，带你回到维京时代！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多精彩内容！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897590/extras/c4663710db1fed69e9e77fc2639bb3bd.avif?t=1771452519\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>开发者的一句话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你好！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>我叫弗洛里安，是游戏《维京传奇——北欧传奇》的开发者。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这个项目已经筹备了两年多，希望你会喜欢，并让你愿意玩上好几个小时。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>作为项目的独行者，我非常依赖你们的众多反馈来帮助我改进游戏。所有的反馈、评论和意见都会被阅读和欣赏，无论是正面还是负面，以使这款游戏尽可能有趣</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>感谢你对这款游戏的关注！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>弗洛里安</i></p>",
